10:44.262 --> 10:45.957
Come in, Arthur.

10:46.531 --> 10:49.466
Oh, hello. The future's now.

10:49.768 --> 10:54.364
Hello, Vivienne. I remember you
from when I used to live in your womb.

10:57.008 --> 10:58.635
Arthur.

10:59.211 --> 11:01.679
Well, today, Arthur,
we're gonna have a friendly chat.

11:01.847 --> 11:03.371
